					<div class="hero__content__inner" id='navConverter'>
						<h1 class="hero__title">The perfect combination between blockchain and messaging</h1>
						<p class="hero__text">A powerful tool to ensure privacy; a beautiful open source project backed by one of the most enthusiastic community. Steem Messenger is meant for people who only accept the best.</p>
						<a href="/login" class="button button__accent">Try it now</a>
						<a href="/infos/what-is-steem-messenger" class="button hero__button">Learn more</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
