	<!-- Steps -->
	<div class="steps landing__section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Who can use Steem Messenger ?</h2>
			<p>Here's who we can think of, but surely creative people will surprise us.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="steps__inner">
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step__media">
						<img src="../images/undraw_designer.png" class="step__image">
					</div>
					<h4>Programmers</h4>
					<p class="step__text">Developers can create automated scripts that interact with users to send and/or receive informations for their businesses</p>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step__media">
						<img src="../images/undraw_responsive.png" class="step__image">
					</div>
					<h4>Content Creators/Users</h4>
					<p class="step__text">Users can safely engage with everybody on the Steem social network, without needing anything more than your recipient username.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step__media">
						<img src="../images/undraw_creation.png" class="step__image">
					</div>
					<h4>Community Managers</h4>
					<p class="step__text">Every community needs its chat medium. CMs can manage easily their communities with powerful tools designed by curators, for curators</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="expanded landing__section">
		<div class="container">
			<div><center>
				<h2>Choose The Best Plan For You</h2>
				<p>Join over 1 Million of users onto the Steem Social Network !</p></center>
			</div>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="steps__inner">
					<div class="step">
						<div class="price-box">
							<h2 class="pricing-plan">Starter</h2>
							<div class="price">1<small> upvote/week</small></div>
							<p>Basic functionnalities for starter users</p>
							<hr>
							<ul class="pricing-info">
								<li>Maximum security</li>
								<li>100 Kb max/file transfer</li>
							</ul>
							<a href="https://steemconnect.com/sign/vote?author=steem-messenger&permlink=steem-messenger-1-weekly-subscription-post" class="button hero__buttonblack">Get started</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="step">
						<div class="price-box popular">
							<div class="popular-text">Popular</div>
							<h2 class="pricing-plan">Regular</h2>
							<div class="price"><sup class="currency">SBD</sup>1<small>/month</small></div>
							<p>Regular functionnalities for regular users</p>
							<hr>
							<ul class="pricing-info">
								<li>Access to special events</li>
								<li>2 Mb max/file transfer</li>
							</ul>
							<a href="https://steemconnect.com/sign/transfer?to=steem-messenger&amount=1.000%20SBD" class="button button__accent">Get started</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="step">
						<div class="price-box">
							<h2 class="pricing-plan">Plus</h2>
							<div class="price"><sup class="currency">SBD</sup>5<small>/month</small></div>
							<p>Pro functionnalities for experienced users</p>
							<hr>
							<ul class="pricing-info">
								<li>Access to the developers API</li>
								<li>10 Mb max/file transfer</li>
							</ul>
							<a href="https://steemconnect.com/sign/transfer?to=steem-messenger&amount=5.000%20SBD" class="button hero__buttonblack">Get started</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>			
		</div>
	</div>


	<!-- Expanded sections -->
	<div class="expanded landing__section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="expanded__inner">
				<div class="expanded__media">
					<img src="../images/together.png" class="expanded__image">
				</div>
				<div class="expanded__content">
					<h2 class="expanded__title">Ready for the next-gen messaging experience ?</h2>
					<p class="expanded__text">Steem Messenger is simple, safe, built for steemians, and quite beautiful to use. It is designed with the community, for the community. In a nutshell, you'll never forget that Steem Messenger is the appropriate tool for handling interpersonnal interactions on the Steem network.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<!-- Call To Action -->
	<div class="cta cta--reverse">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="cta__inner">
				<h2 class="cta__title">Get started now</h2>
				<p class="cta__sub cta__sub--center">Try out the latest version !</p>
				<a href="/login" class="button button__accent">Try it now</a>
